snapshot.content:
1.  Build a desktop GUI (2)
2.  \[Maybe this is just me\] I have been unable to get the web interface working from this command in the readme: `uvicorn delta_poker:app --host=0.0.0.0`
3.  Add Scrum Master role and have that role manage players on a team (1)
4.  Expand the capability to persist game state and continue it (1)
5.  CLI exceptions when not connected to server, provide server status (4)
6.  Provide ability to auto-locate server on the LAN (1)
7.  Change "issues" to "user stories" (4)
8.  Add epics (1)
9.  Provide ability to estimate both story points and business value (1)
10.  Provide ability to import stories and team from taiga (3)
11.  Provide ability to export result of a single estimate or all estimates to taiga (3)
